trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeLabelEdit"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.AfterLabelEdit"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeLabelEdit"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.AfterLabelEdit"> </xref> hendelser.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.AfterLabelEdit> event occurs when the user finishes editing the text for a tree node.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.AfterLabelEdit>inntreffer når brukeren er ferdig med å redigere teksten for en trenode.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.AfterLabelEdit>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeLabelEdit> event occurs when the user begins editing the text for a tree node.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeLabelEdit>hendelsen oppstår når brukeren starter redigere teksten for en trenode.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeLabelEdit>

trans-unit.source: A NodeLabelEditEventArgs object specifies the new text to associate with the tree node, the tree node that contains the label to edit, and whether the edit operation has been canceled.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt for NodeLabelEditEventArgs angir nye teksten som skal knyttes trenode trenode som inneholder etiketten for redigering, og om redigeringsoperasjonen er avbrutt.

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling events, see [Events](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om behandling av hendelser [hendelser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs"></xref> class for the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs"> </xref> klasse for den angitte <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Node%2A> property is assigned the `node` parameter value.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Node%2A>egenskapen er tilordnet av `node` parameterverdi.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Node%2A>

trans-unit.source: The tree node containing the text to edit.
trans-unit.target: Trenode som inneholder teksten for redigering.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs"></xref> class for the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref> and the specified text with which to update the tree node label.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs"> </xref> klasse for den angitte <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"> </xref> og den angitte teksten som du kan oppdatere tre noden etiketten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Node%2A> property is assigned the `node` parameter value, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Label%2A> property is assigned the `label` parameter value.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Node%2A>egenskapen er tilordnet de `node` parameterverdien, og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Label%2A>egenskapen er tilordnet av `label` parameterverdi.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Label%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.NodeLabelEditEventArgs.Node%2A>

trans-unit.source: The tree node containing the text to edit.
trans-unit.target: Trenode som inneholder teksten for redigering.

trans-unit.source: The new text to associate with the tree node.
trans-unit.target: Ny teksten som skal knyttes til trenoden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the edit has been canceled.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om endringer har blitt avbrutt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the edit has been canceled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis endringer har blitt avbrutt; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the new text to associate with the tree node.
trans-unit.target: Henter den nye teksten skal knyttes til trenoden.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is `null` if the user presses ESC to cancel the edit or presses ENTER without modifying the label text.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen er `null` Hvis brukeren trykker ESC for å avbryte redigeringen eller trykker ENTER uten å endre etiketteksten.

trans-unit.source: If the user edits the label text, the value of this property is the new label text.
trans-unit.target: Hvis brukeren redigerer etiketteksten, er verdien for denne egenskapen teksten på nytt.

trans-unit.source: This is true even if the final value of edited label text is the same as its original value.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjelder selv om den siste verdien i redigerte etikettekst er lik den opprinnelige verdien.

trans-unit.source: The string value that represents the new <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref> label or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the user cancels the edit.
trans-unit.target: Strengverdien som representerer det nye <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"> </xref> etiketten eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis brukeren avbryter redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the tree node containing the text to edit.
trans-unit.target: Henter trenode som inneholder teksten for redigering.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref> that represents the tree node containing the text to edit.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"> </xref> som representerer trenode som inneholder teksten for redigering.
